# Enterprise Questionnaire Schema (JSON Schema)

> يُستخدم لتخزين ردود Dealix على استبيانات تقييم المؤسسات.

```json
{
  "$schema": "https://json-schema.org/draft/2020-12/schema",
  "$id": "https://dealix.sa/schemas/enterprise_questionnaire.schema.json",
  "title": "Enterprise Questionnaire Response",
  "type": "object",
  "required": ["questionnaire_id", "client", "submitted_at", "answers"],
  "properties": {
    "questionnaire_id": { "type": "string" },
    "client": {
      "type": "object",
      "required": ["name", "sector"],
      "properties": {
        "name": { "type": "string" },
        "sector": { "type": "string" },
        "region": { "type": "string" }
      }
    },
    "submitted_at": { "type": "string", "format": "date-time" },
    "submitted_by": { "type": "string" },
    "answers": {
      "type": "array",
      "items": {
        "type": "object",
        "required": ["question_id", "question", "answer", "classification"],
        "properties": {
          "question_id": { "type": "string" },
          "question": { "type": "string" },
          "answer": { "type": "string" },
          "classification": { "enum": ["D0", "D1", "D2", "D3", "D4", "D5", "D6"] },
          "evidence_refs": { "type": "array", "items": { "type": "string" } },
          "owner": { "type": "string" },
          "needs_legal_review": { "type": "boolean" }
        }
      }
    },
    "status": { "enum": ["draft", "internal_review", "sent", "acknowledged"] },
    "reviewer_notes": { "type": "string" }
  }
}
```

**مثال صف واحد في `data/enterprise/questionnaires.jsonl`:**

```jsonl
{"questionnaire_id":"q-2026-001","client":{"name":"Acme SA","sector":"healthcare","region":"Riyadh"},"submitted_at":"2026-06-03T03:00:00Z","submitted_by":"founder","answers":[{"question_id":"Q01","question":"أين تُخزّن البيانات؟","answer":"في مزود استضافة سحابي (Railway) — يُحدّد region في DPA","classification":"D1","evidence_refs":["docs/enterprise/SECURITY_OVERVIEW_AR.md"],"owner":"founder","needs_legal_review":false}],"status":"internal_review","reviewer_notes":""}
```
